title: Jane Premium t-shirt
description: Our premium T-shirt made from 100% organic Pima cotton is a luxurious all-rounder for every situation, whether for leisure or for work. The slightly fitted design with side vents, a neckline edged with a fine ribbed fabric and a small label at the hem is classically subtle and can be worn with a wide range of outfits. Pima cotton is particularly fine and comfortable - experience a truly special level of comfort and an exceptional look.

title: FRIEDA T-shirt
description: Up close - the argument for certified natural fashion is obvious: A sustainable manufacturing process in accordance with high socio-ecological standards. The argument for high-quality organic cotton, however, is on your skin: The pure material in high-grade single jersey quality (120 g/m²) gives you pleasant wearing comfort. The slightly fitted women's cut provides for room to move, the crew neck of the durable organic shirt comes with a ribbed cuff. Regular fit.

title: KENNETH T-Shirt

title: IGNACIO T-shirt
description: Stripes ahoy! The striped look for lateral thinkers with taste. Once you have been able to appreciate this cool striped T-shirt, you won't want to get rid of it.
